00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
All extensions can have an Options Page that can be accessed by right-clicking on the Extension icon.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
In order to create an Options Page, we simply add an entry to the manifest file that specifies the name of

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:21,000
the HTML page to use as an Options Page. We can then create an HTML page that we want to display in a new tab

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
when the Options Page is requested. We can implement any functionality we desire on this Options Page;

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
in our case, we'll be showing the current goal and giving the user the ability to change the goal and save it

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:59:00,000
and also the ability to reset the current total.

